# EEG Emotion Detection App

A mobile-based application that detects emotional states in real-time using EEG signals and suggests stress-relieving activities.

## 🔍 Overview
- Reads EEG signals via Bluetooth from a headband device
- Classifies emotional states like stress, calm, focus, etc.
- Triggers actions such as breathing exercises when stress is detected
- Dashboard for viewing emotion history and trends

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Flutter (Frontend)
- Python (Signal processing + model training)
- Firebase (Real-time data sync)
- Bluetooth communication module

## 📌 Status
Prototype developed for a personal project. Code and demo will be published soon.
